#. Tag: para
#: details.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although bibliographic collections are not specifically linked to bibtex, "
"the default set of fields is taken from a typical set of bibtex fields. When "
"exporting to bibtex, a property called <emphasis>bibtex</emphasis> is used "
"for each field to define the corresponding bibtex field. If you add an "
"additional field to a bibliography and want to export it to bibtex, be sure "
"to set the <emphasis>bibtex</emphasis> property."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav bibliografske zbirke niso posebej povezane z bibtexom, je privzeti "
"niz polj vzet iz tipičnega niza polj bibtex. Pri izvozu v bibtex se za vsako "
"polje uporabi lastnost, imenovana <emphasis>bibtex</emphasis>, ki definira "
"ustrezno polje bibtex. Če bibliografiji dodate dodatno polje in ga želite "
"izvoziti v bibtex, obvezno nastavite lastnost <emphasis>bibtex</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: details.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; does have some specialized functions for bibliographies. Bibtex "
"string macros can be added, modified, or deleted from within &appname; and "
"the bibtex export gives you the option of expanding the macros. Bibtex "
"citations can be pushed to an external application such as <application>LyX</"
"application> or <application>Kile</application> using the so-called "
"<emphasis><link linkend=\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</link></emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"&appname; ima nekaj specializiranih funkcij za bibliografije. Makre nizov "
"Bibtex lahko dodate, spremenite ali izbrišete znotraj &appname; in izvoz "
"bibtex vam daje možnost razširitve makrov. Navedbe Bibtex je mogoče "
"potisniti v zunanjo aplikacijo, kot je <application>LyX</application> ali "
"<application>Kile</application> s tako imenovanim <emphasis><link linkend="
"\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</link></emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: details.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Book collections can be converted to bibliographies. Default bibtex fields "
"are added, and the bibtex properties are set. This functionality exists "
"primarily to convert old collections, before the bibliography type was "
"separated from the book collection type."
msgstr ""
"Knjižne zbirke je mogoče pretvoriti v bibliografije. Dodana so privzeta "
"polja bibtex in nastavljene so lastnosti bibtexa. Ta funkcionalnost obstaja "
"predvsem za pretvorbo starih zbirk, preden je bil tip bibliografije ločen od "
"tipa knjižne zbirke."

